reviews.review_text: This certification completely transformed my practice. I was struggling to transition from general wellness coaching to Default, and this course gave me the exact framework I needed. The assessment framework module alone was worth the investment. Now I have 8 new clients and finally feel confident in my niche.
Loved the peer feedback. Being able to discuss marketing authentically with peers who 'get it' was invaluable. The handout library is something I still reference weekly. Great ongoing value.

The depth of research behind this curriculum is impressive. Every claim backed by evidence-based practices, which builds massive credibility with clients. The diagnostic framework has become my go-to for intake sessions. Thoroughly evidence-based.

Good certification with practical tools, though some modules felt repetitive. The session planner was excellent, but cultural considerations could use expansion. Worth it if you're new to default, but experienced practitioners might find some sections basic.

Finally, a certification that respects your intelligence. The conceptual model section gave me the conceptual foundation I was missing from my master's program. Now I can confidently explain systems theory to clients and colleagues.
